issue_meta.title: Wolverine (2003) #38
issue_meta.description:
"Origins and Endings"
The entire Marvel Universe holds its collective breath-after all this time, can it be true? Wolverine returns to his "birthplace," the top-secret military installation known as Department H, the site of the original Weapon X project. But what is he looking for...and who is looking for him? Part 3 of 5

next_issue_meta.title: Wolverine (2003) #39
next_issue_meta.description:
"Origins and Endings," Part 4 of 5: The secret is out. Wolverine remembers. Everything. The entire blood-stained tapestry of his long, tortured life. And now that's it's been laid out before him in vivid detail, there's only one question: What's his first move? Well, whatever it is, it's brought him to Russia for an encounter with the legendary warrior known as the Winter Soldier. One thing's for sure -- they're headed for a major turf battle. Question is, can they find common ground?

32 PGS./PARENTAL ADVISORY ...$2.50
